title: Israelgogo
author: Israelgogo
content: Nothing seems to be happening even after several attempts, Rome wasnt built in a day ,it took several effort to make up a city called Rome, if you put effort in something and nothing is happening ,try it tomorrow & the next ,keep pushing it surely ,you will get there ,it will surely pay off one day ,if it takes you several days to save money for a car, one day the money will be complete to acquire the desired car, if you put more effort and never give up on buying the car, someday you will surely buy the car. it took you days and several effort to finally own a car .
